<h2>Personalized Reading Support</h2>
<p>I focus on building the foundational skills necessary for students to not only read, but to understand and enjoy the stories they encounter.</p>

<h3>What We Focus On:</h3>
<ul>
<li><strong>Phonics & Decoding:</strong> Helping younger readers "sound out" words with confidence.</li>
<li><strong>Reading Fluency:</strong> Working on speed, accuracy, and expression while reading aloud.</li>
<li><strong>Comprehension:</strong> Teaching strategies to remember and analyze what was read.</li>
<li><strong>Vocabulary Building:</strong> Expanding the student's "word bank" to improve writing and speaking.</li>
</ul>

